Package: pdn-convers
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Tom Fanning <tom@m0lte.uk>
Recommends: packetnet
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/m0lte/pdn-convers
Description: Packet-radio convers (round-table chat) app package for the Packet.NET node (pdn)
 A ground-up packet-radio convers node — round-table chat for RF and web users,
 joining the worldwide convers network as a single leaf node. Ships as a Packet.NET
 app PACKAGE: pdn discovers it under /usr/share/packetnet/apps/convers and the node
 owner enables it from the control panel. Self-contained: bundles its own .NET
 runtime, so no system runtime is required. Inert without the packetnet node host
 (hence the soft Recommends), but installable standalone.
